subscribe to: $aws/things/my-temp-sensor-1/shadow/get/accepted
request to: $aws/things/my-temp-sensor-1/shadow/get

subscribe to: $aws/things/my-temp-sensor-1/shadow/update/accepted
update: $aws/things/my-temp-sensor-1/shadow/update
{
  "state": {
    "reported": {
      "temperature": 20
    }
  }
}


